   Menu

Welcome to Leafi

   We are an independent catering company with cafés and restaurants at
   prestigious cultural venues. From afternoon tea to Sunday lunch, we
   offer innovative seasonal menus in unique and inspiring spaces. We also
   cater for corporate events, parties and receptions, offering a bespoke
   service in our range of exclusive venues for a truly special occasion.

   Run by a team of expert 'foodies', we source our ingredients from
   small, local suppliers who support our beliefs in fair trade,
   sustainability and the finest quality. All our menus are cooked from
   raw seasonal ingredients on site, and we believe you'll taste the
   difference.


   Find Out More About Us

